        "瞵悍目以旁睞。"
      ],
      "traditional_char": "睞"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "part_of_speech": "verb",
      "meaning": "眺望，向远处看",
      "examples": [
        "极目睐左阔，回顾眺右狭。",
        "必历鉴周睐，求与己宜。"
      ],
      "traditional_char": "睞"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "part_of_speech": "noun",
      "meaning": "眼旁、眼边",
      "examples": [
